text: The Antonov An-26 is soviet built twin-engine transport aircraft. It is used by both airlines and air forces. It is a short takeoff and landing aircraft. It is built under licence in China like Y-7H. An-26 is a modernized variant of An-24. http://www.avionslegendaires.net/avion-militaire/antonov-an-26-curl/ == Bibliography == * == Similar aircraft == * Airtech CN-235 == References == Category:Civil aircraft Category:Soviet & Russian aircraft Category:Soviet military aircraft
